---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SimpleCard from '../../components/cards/SimpleCard.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Platform Ecosystem"
  description="Tools for designing, building, testing, learning from, and sharing programmable biological systems."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950">Platform Ecosystem</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
      Our tools form a modular platform ecosystem for designing, building, testing, learning from,
      and sharing programmable biological systems.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <SimpleCard title="Design - LOICA"
        >Program genetic networks and biological functions before building them.</SimpleCard
      >
      <SimpleCard title="Build - PUDU and BuildCompiler"
        >Translate designs into assembly and automation-ready build plans.</SimpleCard
      >
      <SimpleCard title="Test - Flapjack workflows"
        >Capture experimental data and metadata from engineered systems.</SimpleCard
      >
      <SimpleCard title="Learn - SeqTrainer"
        >Train and benchmark models from standardized data.</SimpleCard
      >
      <SimpleCard title="Infrastructure - SynBioSuite"
        >Connect standards, repositories, and workflows into a reusable platform.</SimpleCard
      >
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
